8049 - Offices of Health Practitioners, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > SONDER CARE LIMITED is an Australian public company. Its operations cover offices of health practitioners, not elsewhere classified. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. SONDER CARE LIMITED is headquartered in Edinburgh North, South Australia. It is headed by chief executive officer & comp sec Richard Chiak Seng Heah. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $34.13 million. Its net loss totalled $5.72 million. SONDER CARE LIMITED forms part of the services industry sector.
